TradeFrame is a job documentation and business management tool for contractors. The App provides features including job tracking, client management, estimates, invoices, photo documentation, GPS tagging, voice notes, progress reports, closeout reports, and analytics.

## 3. Subscription Plans

### Free Tier
- Limited to 1 active job
- Banner advertisements are displayed
- Core features available with limited capacity

### TradeFrame Pro (Monthly or Annual)
- Unlimited jobs
- Full access to estimates, invoices, PDF reports, analytics, and data export
- Ad-free experience
- Prices are displayed in the App at time of purchase and may vary by region

### Auto-Renewal
- Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current billing period
- Your Apple ID account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period at the same rate
- You can manage and cancel subscriptions in your device Settings → [Your Name] → Subscriptions

### Free Trial
- If a free trial is offered, any unused portion is forfeited when you purchase a subscription

